data.description: Welcome to 436 Midridge Lane in Pelham, Alabama—a charming 3-bed, 2-bath home zoned for Pelham Schools. With 1360 sq ft of main-level living, this low-maintenance property comes without HOA fees. The kitchen was recently remodeled in 2023, and a new roof was added in 2022. The HVAC system is 5 years young, and the water heater is 3-4 years old. With no foundation issues, this home ensures stability and peace of mind. Located conveniently in Pelham, near schools and amenities, this residence offers a delightful blend of comfort and style. Don't miss the chance to make 436 Midridge Lane your home sweet home.  ***NOTE: More pictures to come. Property will be landscaped, pressure washed, and deep cleaned prior to going "Active".***
